room_title: Escape room "The Spell" by Escape Room Brunswick in Brunswick
room_description: In a sleepy little town at the edge of the deep Maine woods, something is amiss.. people are getting very sick, and no one understands why! The mayor suspects that a witch that lives deep in the woods has put a curse over the town after she was banished  years ago. He is looking for a group of brave souls to break into her cabin and retrieve her Book of Secrets so that the Spell may be broken. Are you and your team up for the task??
